{"source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "kind": "quest-reference-unresolved", "message": "quest reference could not be mapped to one canonical questKey", "equipmentId": 96, "equipmentName": "零式艦戦21型(熟練)", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B%28%E7%86%9F%E7%B7%B4%29", "methodIndex": 1, "reference": {"rawName": "マンスリー任務『精鋭「艦戦」隊の新編成』により、零式艦戦21型から機種転換することでも入手が可能。詳細は21型のページを参照。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}}
{"source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "kind": "quest-reference-unresolved", "message": "quest reference could not be mapped to one canonical questKey", "equipmentId": 96, "equipmentName": "零式艦戦21型(熟練)", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B%28%E7%86%9F%E7%B7%B4%29", "methodIndex": 2, "reference": {"rawName": "この機種転換はマンスリー任務であるものの、定期的な入手方法がクォータリー任務しかない*3消費アイテム「熟練搭乗員」を消費する特殊な任務なので、定期的にクリア出来るのは3ヶ月に1回のみ。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}}
{"source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "kind": "quest-reference-unresolved", "message": "quest reference could not be mapped to one canonical questKey", "equipmentId": 96, "equipmentName": "零式艦戦21型(熟練)", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B%28%E7%86%9F%E7%B7%B4%29", "methodIndex": 3, "reference": {"rawName": "後のアップデートにて熟練搭乗員を入手できる(選択報酬)クォータリー任務が追加された（2018/11/16『泊地周辺海域の安全確保を徹底せよ！』と2018/12/07『空母戦力の投入による兵站線戦闘哨戒』）ので、", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}}
{"source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "kind": "quest-reference-unresolved", "message": "quest reference could not be mapped to one canonical questKey", "equipmentId": 96, "equipmentName": "零式艦戦21型(熟練)", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B%28%E7%86%9F%E7%B7%B4%29", "methodIndex": 4, "reference": {"rawName": "3つのクォータリー任務を全てこなせば事実上1か月に1回クリアできるようになった。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}}
{"source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "kind": "quest-reference-unresolved", "message": "quest reference could not be mapped to one canonical questKey", "equipmentId": 96, "equipmentName": "零式艦戦21型(熟練)", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B%28%E7%86%9F%E7%B7%B4%29", "methodIndex": 5, "reference": {"rawName": "ただし、熟練搭乗員を消費する任務はこの他にも多くあるので、何を優先すべきかはよく考えること。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}}
{"source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "kind": "quest-reference-unresolved", "message": "quest reference could not be mapped to one canonical questKey", "equipmentId": 96, "equipmentName": "零式艦戦21型(熟練)", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B%28%E7%86%9F%E7%B7%B4%29", "methodIndex": 7, "reference": {"rawName": "但しこの21型を機種転換する任務、後述するマンスリー零式艦戦52型(熟練)転換・岩本隊転換・岩井隊転換の任務ツリーが発生するトリガーとして最低一度は達成しておかないといけない点には注意。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}}
{"source": "wikiwiki-equipment-detail", "kind": "quest-reference-unresolved", "message": "quest reference could not be mapped to one canonical questKey", "equipmentId": 96, "equipmentName": "零式艦戦21型(熟練)", "sourceUrl": "https://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%8F%E8%89%A6%E6%88%A621%E5%9E%8B%28%E7%86%9F%E7%B7%B4%29", "methodIndex": 8, "reference": {"rawName": "故に最低1機は熟練搭乗員を用いた機種転換で作成する必要がある。", "questKey": null, "questCode": null, "questName": null, "status": "unresolved", "evidence": "method-text"}}
